A beautiful love story, shared with permission. 

May Ibiza Retreatment, Lunch time. 

Bradley : T, I have highly confidential info. Can you keep a secret? 
Me : YES 
Brad : I have a ring, I’m going to propose in Mallorca, after we leave here. 
Me : oh my oh my pls pls pls do it here ((cue — carry on for way too long trying to convince)). 

Brad : no no she won’t want that, she doesn’t. 
Me : but but but and and and ….and and …. then we can all celebrate you. 
Brad : no no, she won’t want that. 
Me : ok - hear you. If at any point you change you mind, please know I’m here. Use me, will do anything to support. 

Closing circle. 
Closing dinner. 
Closing party. 
JOY. 
No proposal. Sigh. Okkkkkkk. 

Departure day - integrative movement led by the exquisite @aimee_mere and @rawbabysugar - FULL celebration. 

Brad grabs me RIGHT after - locks me dead in the eyes - T I NEED YOU. 
Can you help me? 

Me : HERE (quietly praying that I am reporting for duty). 
B : I’m going to go get the ring in my bag at the check out desk - can you distract Sylvie for me? 

Absolutely. 

Turn to Sylvie - “want to go to the ocean and do a final dip cleanse before we part ways?”

UMMmmm, YES. 

We head down to the ocean with a small group, no bathing suits. Oh well. 
We get in nude. Even better. 
The water is cold sparkly navy blue and absolutely glorious. 
We do some clearing things - wombs, cords, giggling, shining, joyful laughing. 

Brad comes down with a concerned look on his face. 
Sylvie - can I talk to you? 

She steps out and Brad walks her to the side. I silently slip my bare bum out of the water and set up behind a rock. 
And capture this moment. 
Oh how I love the 🌕!!! 

Congratulations @sylvieec and Brad! You are made of magic, we all adore you both and it was a true gift and honor be a part of this moment - and thank you are allowing us all to take part of your joy!!  
Here’s to you.  
And all of us too. 
I love you. I love you. I love you too.

“You will know exactly what to do when you are present, always.

As such, just because you are not at Peace with a situation does not mean you cannot still be at Peace with yourself. You are not the situation. Situations should have no bearing on your Peace…. unless you allow them to. You did not come to this world for situational Peace. Peace does not need a modifier. You came to this world to come to Peace with yourself and, as a result, to serve from that Peace through your Divine essence. “ - The Freedom Transmissions via Carissa Schumacher.

Sit tall, heart upright, soften the skin on your shoulders, back.
Inhale love, exhale Peace. 
Repeat. Repeat. Repeat.

Lots of new @theclass on link in bio - playlists, Retreatments (more incoming fall winter spring) new programs, audio series, breathwork, giggles, sighs, reunions, passages, paths, bucking broncos (not actually), smiles. 
I hope you enjoy. With love.

It is all a love story, in the end.

The opening of love, the releasing of.
The void period.
Space waiting to be filled with love.

Reweaving into, the unweaving from.
Again.

Threading through the heart with the inhale.
Unstitching (grief) in the exhale, let go. 

Place your hand on your heart, feel your heart in your hands.  Soften. Giggle. Smile. Do the most loving thing. 

It was all a love story, in the end. 
@theclass

Thank you for moving energy with me for all these years.
For continually inviting me to show up.
With love. x

oooo jim james. 
heart and soul.
song. reverberations. 
as prayer. 

:: notes :: 

there is a remedy to what is hard, it is the healing. 
use compassion as the compass. 
and sincere humility. 
sometimes it is as simple as impulse control. 
respect the complexities of the human condition. 
embrace vulnerability. 
cry every time you are able.
the tears are the heart healing.  
hug for a moment longer.

be honest. you will learn to respect yourself. and your word. so you trust yourself.

life is too short to hold onto resentments. 
take personal inventory.
and responsibly for your part. 
be sincere. 
respect relationship.
try to do the right thing.
make amends w out harming. 
right relationships when able. 
you will know how to if they matter. 
when not able simply do the most loving thing. 

play ⭐️ in the field of song with those who you have been healing alongside with. giggle laugh yelp weep hold hands and be sure to make space to sing and play. 

when in doubt put your head down to your soul and listen hard.  

heart + soul. 

in there, you will know.

Embodiment as an act of love. 
Truth love strength humility honor thru the field.
Treat experience with reverence. 
Piercing the scared heart. 

Eclipse season as explained via Pink Floyd + visual diary. 

“All that you touch
And all that you see
All that you taste
All you feel
And all that you love
And all that you hate
All you distrust
All you save
And all that you give
And all that you deal
And all that you buy
Beg, borrow or steal
And all you create
And all you destroy
And all that you do
And all that you say
And all that you eat
And everyone you meet (everyone you meet)
And all that you slight
And everyone you fight
And all that is now
And all that is gone
And all that’s to come
And everything under the sun is in tune
But the sun is eclipsed by the moon”. 

Like a hot wire running thru the system, realigning. We via @theclass worked right that eclipse window on The Retreatment.

Let go, let go, when you think you have let go, let go again.
Then notice how it feels to be without it. 
Rest rest rest rest and digest.
